---------------------------------------------------------------------

OpenH: Programming and Execution Model for Applications 
on Heterogeneous Hybrid Platforms

---------------------------------------------------------------------

Creators: Simon Farrelly and Ravi Reddy Manumachu

---------------------------------------------------------------------

To build and install:

1). cd <hclaffinity root directory>

Replace '<hclaffinity root directory>' by the directory 
where hclaffinity is downloaded.

2). Set the OpenACC environment.

$ source setacc.sh

3). make

4). To run tests,

export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$(pwd)/openhinstall/lib64:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH

The tests and applications are installed in the openhinstall directory.

